<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr>  you (Krilen) my friend (/sarcasm off) happens to be someone that wants to do the class harm. <hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
